        <h2 class="section-title anim anim-right delay-1">NaturalTag&trade;</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle anim anim-right delay-2">A food-grade molecular marker embedded into your product at source. Not applied after. Not added later. Formulated in. NaturalTag&trade; is your product's permanent molecular identity.</p>
        <div class="tech-features">
          <div class="tech-feature anim anim-right delay-1"><div class="tech-feature-num">01</div><div><h4>Food-Grade Composition</h4><p>Composed entirely of inactivated probiotic Lactobacillus species already used in food production</p></div></div>
          <div class="tech-feature anim anim-right delay-2"><div class="tech-feature-num">02</div><div><h4>Non-GMO</h4><p>No genetic modification. Naturally occurring organisms, regulatory-compatible worldwide</p></div></div>
          <div class="tech-feature anim anim-right delay-3"><div class="tech-feature-num">03</div><div><h4>PCR-Detectable</h4><p>Designed for detection by quantitative PCR at trace concentrations downstream</p></div></div>
          <div class="tech-feature anim anim-right delay-4"><div class="tech-feature-num">04</div><div><h4>Batch-Level Traceability</h4><p>Each production batch receives a unique marker combination for full chain-of-custody</p></div></div>
        </div>
